                  "LCS"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Monocromatic \"LADON\"  photon  beam  obtained  by",
                " compton  backscattering  of  laser light by electrons",
                " circulating in storage ring.  The  energy  resolution",
                " varied from 4.3 to 9.0%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The target was helium gas at a pressure  of  30  bars.",
                " the  target  container  was  a  very  thin  (0.16 mm)",
                " aluminium  cylinder  of  15  cm  length  and  1.5  cm",
                " diameter, with two lexan end caps."
              ]
            }
          ],
