              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Direct measurement  of  the  reaction  cross  section.",
                " background   contributions   come   both   from   the",
                " interactions  of  photons with the detector materials",
                " and from the bremsstrahlung  component  of  the  beam",
                " were  evaluated  by alternating empty and full target",
                " and by direct measurements with turning off the laser",
                " light and running the bremsstrahlung beam alone."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Statistical errors."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The absolute  total cross section for the He-4(g,p)H-3",
                " reaction has been measured in the g-ray energy region",
                " between  28.6 and 58.1 MeV with a monocromatic photon",
                " beam and a nearly 4PI proton detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
